HARRY ROQUE: Filipinos should be ashamed as PH tops w/ most COVID19 cases in SEA.

WTF. THE FILIPINO PEOPLE ARE NOT RUNNING THIS COUNTRY—THE ADMIN IS.

They make the policies; they make the decisions; they already have the funds.

So, they better take some effin' responsibility! https://t.co/7wHabPSAYF
